## How the Speaking Works

```kotlin
override fun onRobotFocusGained(qiContext: QiContext) {
    val say = SayBuilder.with(qiContext)  // Connect to robot
        .withText("Hello World!")          // Set the text to speak
        .build()                           // Create the action
    say.run()                              // Execute — Pepper speaks
}
```

`onRobotFocusGained` is called automatically by QiSDK when Pepper is ready and the app has control. To change what Pepper says, simply change the text inside `withText("...")`.
